snippet.description:
Subscribe for more GTLive action! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 
The Megaman Game You NEVER Played! ► http://bit.ly/1WOrLHk
Trippin' Balls in New Mario 64! ►► http://bit.ly/2fBbjOx

We got a brand new system - the NES Classic Edition console. Okay, so maybe new isn't the right descriptor. Today we're revisiting the classics - with some added challenges of your choice! You send us your sabotages - blindfolds, sharing the controller, playing upside down... you name it and we'll try to make it happen.

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive

More GTLive Videos:
Mario Maker's Pumpkin Head Challenge ► http://bit.ly/2g4Riy5
Cat Mario: CatPat's Revenge! ►► http://bit.ly/2f8ECEd
STRANGE Life Goals! - Mario Maker ►► http://bit.ly/1V7SP6N
I Wanna Be the Guy - Hardest Game Evar ► http://bit.ly/22fm4Wj
Kaizo Mario: Death Awaits (Part 1) ►► http://bit.ly/1WO6pdK
Growing Bigger than Everyone - Zlap.io ► http://bit.ly/2eHzbxI

Don't have much time but need a quick fix? Check out some of our highlight episodes for hilarious moments from our live streams. Here are a few to get you started.

HiLite: Flappy Mario Maker? JUST DO IT! ► http://bit.ly/1Oq8GvE
HiLite: FNAF Theorists Surprised By Scott! ► http://bit.ly/1Jrlm3i
HiLite: Mega Man Marshmallow Challenge! ► http://bit.ly/1OHe3kb

Thanks to David Keller for allowing us use of his sound FX:
http://consumingfireartisticcreations.weebly.com/
snippet.title: You TROLL MatPat! - Retro Sabotage Returns
